3/ While Roy worked on the food, Eric asked me to figure out launch strategy, brand, name, etc. I named it Kogi (kōgi like bulgogi/not gee).
2/ @kogibbq was started by Roy (chef), Mark (mgmt), Caroline (ops) & Eric (photo/ops). Mark had concept for a truck, Roy had idea for taco.
